title: Bujtina e Gjelit
description: Simple accommodations in a property featuring traditional Albanian style, a restaurant & a pool.
hotelDescription:
This old-school hotel and restaurant with traditional Albanian shingles and brickwork, is a 3-minute walk away from a bus stop and 2 km from the exhibits of Muzeu Historik Kombëtar.
 The simple, old-world rooms and a sole suite provide Albanian textiles, wood-beam ceilings and hardwood floors, as well as Wi-Fi, satellite TV and minibars. Room service is available.
 Common areas feature rustic wood beams and cobblestone floors. There's an informal restaurant with a brick oven and outdoor seating, an outdoor pool with sunloungers, and free parking. Hiking, BBQs and fruit-picking are available at the hotel's off-site farm.
